FDD.Issue:
#### **Issue**
• The supply fan transducer has failed in the "on" position.
FDD.Task:
#### **Task**
• Check the status transducer.

• Repair or replace as needed.

• Confirm proper status feedback is provided.
FDD.Operational Impacts:
#### **Operational Impacts**
This issue can lead to:

• Falsely giving the appearance that there is an override or that the fan has failed on.

• Lower building data quality, which impacts the analysis of other faults.
FDD.Conditions:
#### **Conditions**
• Supply fan status stays on when the fan is commanded on and commanded off.

• When the fan command is off, the static pressure drops below 0.1" w.c., suggesting the fan is truly off.
